full_text: Screened by NARA, 6/29/2023 WITNESS STATEMENT MR. /MS. MARIA JUANA ALVARENGA IS ILLITERATE IN HER NATIVE LANGUAGE AND THEREFORE UNABLE TO SIGN HER NAME. I WITNESSED HER PLACING AN "X" ON THE FOLLOWING DOCUMENTS (S). FORM I-821 FORM I-104 FORM I-765 2 FORMS FD-258 I DECLARE UNDER PENALTY OF PERJURY THAT THE ABOVE STATEMENT IS TRUE AND CORRECT, EXECUTED THIS 13 DAY OF JUNE , 1991, IN HUNTINGTON PARK, COUNTY OF LOS ANGELES, STATE OF CALIFORNIA. Kashay KATHY ALFRED defred ATTORNEY AT LAW PRIVATE IMMIGRATION AGENCY 2407 RANDOLPH ST. HUNTINGTON PARK, CA 90255 Q.D.E. 00-903-05
